Package: Pviz
Type: Package
Title: Peptide Annotation and Data Visualization using Gviz
Version: 0.99.1
Author: Mike Jiang, Raphael Gottardo
Maintainer: Renan Sauteraud <rsautera@fhcrc.org>
Description: Pviz adapts the Gviz package for protein information and data.
    Uses the PEP.db, HIV.db and pepStat packages to obtain annotation and
    intensity data on desired proteins and allows their display via Gviz.
License: Artistic-2.0
Depends:
    R(>= 3.0.0),
    Gviz(>= 1.7.10)
Imports:
    biovizBase,
    GenomicRanges,
    IRanges,
    data.table,
    methods,
    RColorBrewer
Suggests:
    knitr,
    PEP.db
biocViews: Microarray, Visualisation
VignetteBuilder: knitr
